to seize me.

30:18.567 --> 30:20.152
Okay?

30:24.782 --> 30:27.201
I’m just trying
to get through this.

30:27.284 --> 30:29.078
So am I.

30:30.663 --> 30:33.457
We’re not that different,
Margaret.

30:33.541 --> 30:35.084
We’re not like other people.

30:35.167 --> 30:37.294
