this is the only one we have.

30:40.631 --> 30:44.552
Sometimes I think,
what if it’s not enough?

30:46.095 --> 30:48.305
I just want it
to mean something.

30:51.058 --> 30:54.728
Besides, you know, it’s just us.

30:56.438 --> 30:58.732
